data.description: Welcome to 1197 Walnut Street! This home has a BRAND NEW eat-in kitchen and full bathroom on the first floor. Oversized living room with decorative fireplace, mudroom, and front entry way round out the first floor. Original hardwood floors, pocket doors, and intricate staircase that boasts with character through this home! Sprawling front porch with more than half of it enclosed to keep away the bugs while you're enjoying the outdoors. Paved parking behind the home, off of the alley. Loads of storage throughout the home! Four large bedrooms on the second floor with another full bathroom.  Walk up finished attic allows for a fifth bedroom, in-home office, or playroom for the kids! A lot of new windows throughout the home that were just installed this summer. Walking distance to Stoneboro Memorial Park, Lakeview Schools, and downtown Stoneboro.
